snippet.textDisplay: In the past couple years I have put in a golf simulator (DIY to keep cost down) and a home gym.  My job is busy and with 2 little kids my free time is limited. Being able to have a quick range session, play 18 holes in 45 minutes on the sim and work out from home has been great.  Being in the Northern United States we lose 5 months of golf to cold weather.  Due to being able to practice and play more after my sim my handicap improved from 12 to 6 in the past 2 years.  I would highly recommend building your own sim.  There is a great website called golf simulator forums with tons of information and people that will answer your questions on completing your sim.

Hive meanings
The word hive is most recognizable as a place where bees live, but it can be a verb that means to move together as one, like a swarm of bees. It can also describe storing a lot of things in a confined space, the way bees are packed into a hive.
